{141}{}{好主意。但请记住-如果这些生物开始咬你，我只会看节目到最后再回去。我不想白白浪费弹药。 -- Good thought. But keep in mind - if these creatures start to chew you, I'll just watch the show to the end and go back. I don't want to waste ammunition in vain.}
