#{160}{}{An old,, but reliable rifle. I bought it at the Wind of War. They usually keep good weapons for themselves and sell whatever is left. I was lucky to catch one of the best among those that were on the stock. However, this one too has flaws. As for gunner... Yes, I have to count every shot, because bullets aren't cheap. That's how I trained.}
{160}{}{一把旧的，但可靠的步枪。我冒着战争的危险买了它。他们通常为自己保留好武器，把剩下的都卖掉。我很幸运地抓住了存货中最好的一个。然而，这个也有缺陷。至于枪手。。。是的，我得数一数每一发子弹，因为子弹不便宜。我就是这样训练的。 -- An old,, but reliable rifle. I bought it at the Wind of War. They usually keep good weapons for themselves and sell whatever is left. I was lucky to catch one of the best among those that were on the stock. However, this one too has flaws. As for gunner... Yes, I have to count every shot, because bullets aren't cheap. That's how I trained.}
